Extension : OW Translate
Requires : eZ Publish 4.x.x (not tested on 3.X)
Author : Open Wide <http://www.openwide.fr>

What is OW Translate?
-------------------

OW Translate is an ezpublish extension which supplies several tools 
 - A generator of files of translation for all languages of your site
 - An interface allowing to administer each of these translations

